the frame. </div><br /><br />Yep, without an Scanline IRQ you have to constantly wait, that is unless you have some interesting timed code.<br /><br /><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">But, this means that the BG is off, and is turned on after the sprite-0 hit. So is that possible ?<br />If it's not, I've the idea to put 9 sprites at the last status bar's row, and using $2002.5 trigger as explained in the parallel topic. Would it works with most emulators ?</div>
